  "page": "Jeyne Smallwood",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\"><img alt=\"House Smallwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/50px-House_Smallwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/75px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/100px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Jeyne Smallwood</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\"><img alt=\"House Smallwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/50px-House_Smallwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/75px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/100px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Three Jeynes by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/af/Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/af/Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Three_Jeynes_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Jeyne Smallwood (left) with Jeyne Mooton and Jeyne Merryweather by coldraindropsss ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\">House Smallwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_121_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">121&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jeyne Smallwood</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\">House Smallwood</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Smallwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_Ball\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day Ball\">Maiden's Day Ball</a> was held at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> to find a second wife and new queen for King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>. Many <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maidens</a> across <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> came to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> in hopes of marrying the young king. Jeyne was one of the many maidens who suffered what was called the \"<a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_curse\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day curse\">Maiden's Day curse</a>\" by being injured or scandalized after the ball was announced. In Jeyne's case, a rumor spread that she, <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Merryweather\" title=\"Jeyne Merryweather\">Jeyne Merryweather</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Mooton\" title=\"Jeyne Mooton\">Jeyne Mooton</a> (known as the \"<a href=\"/index.php/Three_Jeynes\" title=\"Three Jeynes\">three Jeynes</a>\") liked to dress in <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>'s garb, visiting the <a href=\"/index.php/Brothel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brothel\">brothels</a> along the <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_Silk\" title=\"Street of Silk\">Street of Silk</a> to kiss and fondle the women there as if they were boys. It is possible that this was a rumor fabricated by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, who wished to promote his <a href=\"/index.php/Myrielle_Peake\" title=\"Myrielle Peake\">own daughter</a> as Aegon III's second queen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Smallwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jeyne's relation to the head of her house, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Joseth_Smallwood\" title=\"Joseth Smallwood\">Joseth Smallwood</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a>, is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Smallwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Jeyne_Smallwood\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Jeyne Smallwood</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; B